  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<i>Switch Box</i>\" is a 2D pixel-art puzzle platformer. In an unfamiliar world, you must interact with the environment and utilize tools to solve challenges, overcome obstacles, and ultimately discover the path back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal is to forge ahead and clear the path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/3a9f73b4d7143e440b2e77ccf33230a5.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/3a9f73b4d7143e440b2e77ccf33230a5.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/3a9f73b4d7143e440b2e77ccf33230a5.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the items around you to pass through obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/e538d587cee997eb044fdcc3ed84a0b2.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/e538d587cee997eb044fdcc3ed84a0b2.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/e538d587cee997eb044fdcc3ed84a0b2.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seize the right moment to move forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/59fbefc81a04fc5e0ec740bea5cdb25d.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/59fbefc81a04fc5e0ec740bea5cdb25d.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/59fbefc81a04fc5e0ec740bea5cdb25d.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flip the switch and proceed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/036d4ec20841a0ebee1b681dd567c62f.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/036d4ec20841a0ebee1b681dd567c62f.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/036d4ec20841a0ebee1b681dd567c62f.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expected, yet unexpected.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/f683e8eb877fa963e3f6bc069f0019b3.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/f683e8eb877fa963e3f6bc069f0019b3.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/f683e8eb877fa963e3f6bc069f0019b3.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge a path through peril.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/5989fea578212f0a46a568f78f9a47a1.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/5989fea578212f0a46a568f78f9a47a1.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/5989fea578212f0a46a568f78f9a47a1.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the goal to reach the next stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/48015406a9f81eebad0daf64e4bf2f85.poster.avif?t=1756371111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/48015406a9f81eebad0daf64e4bf2f85.webm?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282350/extras/48015406a9f81eebad0daf64e4bf2f85.mp4?t=1756371111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
